        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Integrate the ACE-Step 1.5 Turbo unified inference API by first obtaining API keys from the provider dashboard. Use standard HTTP clients like Axios or Requests in Python, ensuring error handling for retries and timeouts. For asynchronous workflows, implement webhook callbacks or message queues such as RabbitMQ. Test integration in a staging environment with synthetic traffic to validate response times and error rates before going live."
          }
        ]
      },
